**Problem:** All 4 route components are **eagerly imported** at lines 2–6. Every byte of `ProductDetails`, `InventoryList`, and `ShowHistoryLogs` loads on the `/products` page even though they're never used there. This is a primary driver of your 10.6s FCP.

```tsx
