## Fix #4 — `index.html` — Quick FCP Win

**Problem:** No resource hints. The browser discovers `main.tsx` late in parsing.

```html
<!-- index.html — BEFORE <head> -->
<title>product-dashboard</title>
```

```html
<!-- index.html — AFTER, add inside <head> -->
<title>product-dashboard</title>
<link rel="modulepreload" href="/src/main.tsx" />
```

