## Fix #5 — `ProductList` / `ProductDetails` components (image fixes)

The audit flagged **281 KiB** from offscreen images and **154 KiB** from non-next-gen formats. You'll need to apply these in whichever component renders your product images:

```tsx
// Wherever you render product <img> tags — BEFORE
<img src={product.imageUrl} alt={product.name} />

// AFTER — lazy load + explicit dimensions prevent layout shift (CLS)
<img
  src={product.imageUrl}
  alt={product.name}
  width={300}
  height={200}
  loading="lazy"
  decoding="async"
/>
```

For next-gen format support, serve `.webp` from your API/CDN, or use a `<picture>` element with a WebP source and a JPEG fallback.

